{"tid":2389751,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK 線上演唱會《THE SHOW》精彩落幕！粗估收入至少百億韓元","createTime":"2021-02-01T06:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T11:50:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"91f8f01885a5b01f8223a006d8434537e1501532","tid":2389751,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:13:31.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK 昨晚在《THE SHOW》上結合尖端技術，首度公開多首精彩的表演，在網路上掀起了熱烈討論。大家都有看這場線上演唱會嗎？<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK 昨晚舉行了線上演唱會《YG PALM STAGE - 2021 BLACKPINK: THE SHOW》（以下簡稱 THE SHOW），以滿滿的 19 首表演填滿整場演出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d70e266ddd1b42ff011b2785aca4b175/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-01/133413-895609.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d70e266ddd1b42ff011b2785aca4b175%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-01%2F133413-895609.jpg&h=9ff39135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1585eb460512268ef76105712cbb34d7/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-01/133413-895610.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1585eb460512268ef76105712cbb34d7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-01%2F133413-895610.jpg&h=b9235095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當天 BLACKPINK 在現場樂隊的伴奏下，透過高音質的技術輸出成員們的現場歌聲，帶來充滿臨場感的效果。以 &ldquo;Kill this Love&rdquo; 開場後，BLACKPINK 除了帶來 &ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo;、&ldquo;Whistle&rdquo;、&ldquo;BOOMBAYAH&rdquo;⋯⋯等多首出道四年多來的經典主打歌，和正規一輯〈THE ALBUM〉中收錄的歌曲外，還首度在現場表演了成員 Ros&eacute; 的個人歌曲 &ldquo;Gone&rdquo;，以及和 Lady Gaga 合作的 &ldquo;Sour Candy&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ef32eea812aa301fed4a6ad106249a36/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-01/133413-895611.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ef32eea812aa301fed4a6ad106249a36%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-01%2F133413-895611.png&h=9ea0a8b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別的是，在 BLACKPINK 的官方 YouTube 頻道登場的《THE SHOW》，並開放付費會員參與。根據統計，約有 28 萬人申請成為付費會員，創下了 YG 旗下女團單一演唱會的最多觀眾數紀錄；即使每人都只夠買最便宜的套票，這場演出的收入仍輕易地突破了 100 億韓元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_385906cdd4594e7a72cdad017d7da955/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-01/133413-895612.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_385906cdd4594e7a72cdad017d7da955%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-01%2F133413-895612.png&h=03e7297d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這同時，BLACKPINK 的官方 YouTube 頻道訂閱數，也隨著演唱會消息而急速上升，自消息公布至今變增加了 270 萬人，關於演唱會的主題標籤 &ldquo;#THESHOWToday&rdquo; 也在推特趨勢上奪冠，四位成員也全數打入前十名內。<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment、sooyaaa__、roses_are_rosie、jennierubyjane）"},{"pid":"af5f12a97436a3164a10ebf5b41616593233a0fa","tid":2389751,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"3f429c0fdb79bacb313734a87de298263e1c8919","tid":2389751,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"622d661c16a58f5b24c2ecf1d47f7be82da24980","tid":2389751,"uid":12782,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"8918dcdb774832a495f15b6366ea095a19da1537","tid":2389751,"uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"可惜連登仲有好多免費仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係收得仲多錢"},{"pid":"af2653b813e405d7e80cae4dc189d45d3cb8eb30","tid":2389751,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:18:28.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487d7ab0735b28f7a8d9d1a2e64f79841f597e6b","tid":2389751,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:19:26.000Z","m